1
00:01:30,149 --> 00:01:32,829
[Episode 22]

2
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:37,169
Our marriage has always been a lie.

3
00:01:37,169 --> 00:01:41,265
You know that you'll use me more than once.

4
00:01:41,265 --> 00:01:43,919
So, why do you keep on lying to yourself...

5
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:46,080
and why do you want to make things difficult for me?

6
00:01:53,805 --> 00:01:55,605
Please go out.

7
00:01:56,204 --> 00:01:58,384
I want to be by myself for a while.

8
00:02:21,452 --> 00:02:24,600
Rong Le! Rong Le.

9
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:27,542
Don't scare me, Rong Le!

10
00:02:40,011 --> 00:02:43,311
Sir. Sir?

11
00:02:45,788 --> 00:02:48,987
What's wrong with my wife? When can she wake up?

12
00:02:49,471 --> 00:02:53,721
General Fu, your wife's illness is very rare.

13
00:02:53,721 --> 00:02:58,242
Although her pulse is weak, it's not so weak that she'll lose consciousness.

14
00:02:58,243 --> 00:03:01,420
I think the reason she fainted is a psychological factor.

15
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:05,700
This kind of illness can only be treated on the mental plane.

16
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:08,309
I can only give her some medicine for nourishment...

17
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:10,627
and help her to recuperate.

18
00:03:10,628 --> 00:03:13,125
As for whether or not she can wake up,

19
00:03:13,126 --> 00:03:16,973
it'll be up to fate to decide.

20
00:03:21,052 --> 00:03:23,543
Thank you, Sir.

21
00:03:24,544 --> 00:03:27,164
- See him out.
- Yes, General Fu.

22
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,040
Let me.

23
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:43,665
♫ I don't think that we will be talking anymore after this ♫

24
00:03:43,665 --> 00:03:45,985
♫ We have been through so much ♫

25
00:03:45,986 --> 00:03:47,166
When will she wake?

26
00:03:47,167 --> 00:03:50,247
♫ Why didn't I realize it sooner? ♫

27
00:03:51,751 --> 00:03:56,879
♫ My heart was bleeding when I saw you leaving me ♫

28
00:03:56,900 --> 00:04:03,600
♫ There was once happiness as grand
as three thousand rivers and mountains ♫

29
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:10,172
♫ Although we haven't known each other for long,
I already miss you so ♫

30
00:04:10,173 --> 00:04:13,383
♫ Do you dare to...? ♫

31
00:04:14,509 --> 00:04:17,896
When Brother Wuyou rushed there to save Princess Rong Le today,

32
00:04:17,896 --> 00:04:22,936
I'd never seen him so anxious and agitated before.

33
00:04:23,969 --> 00:04:27,090
I think Brother Wuyou still cares about Princess Rong Le.

34
00:04:27,090 --> 00:04:30,370
It's impossible for him to fall in love with Miss Sun in Qingzhou.

35
00:04:30,986 --> 00:04:33,433
Brother Wuyou won't shilly-shally like that.

36
00:04:33,433 --> 00:04:37,966
Wuyou's mind is not something that we can comprehend.

37
00:04:37,967 --> 00:04:41,134
I think there must be some misunderstanding between them.

38
00:04:41,134 --> 00:04:43,420
When I went fishing with Princess Rong Le today,

39
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:47,135
she was so shaken when she heard that Brother Wuyou was coming back.

40
00:04:47,136 --> 00:04:50,385
She still cares about Brother Wuyou for sure.

41
00:04:50,386 --> 00:04:53,604
They love each other, but they cannot be together.

42
00:04:53,605 --> 00:04:56,105
It's so unfortunate.

43
00:04:57,873 --> 00:05:00,453
It's hard to find love that reciprocates this world.

44
00:05:00,454 --> 00:05:04,030
They love each other but they cannot be together.

45
00:05:04,030 --> 00:05:07,055
It would have been better off if they had remained as strangers since the beginning.

46
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:12,212
So, we can't make the same mistake as them.

47
00:05:12,212 --> 00:05:16,471
We have to be together forever until we are old and gray.

48
