00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:52,777
♫ Although we haven't known each other for long,
I already miss you so ♫

54
00:05:53,529 --> 00:06:00,359
♫ Do you dare to face the possible truth? ♫

55
00:06:01,714 --> 00:06:06,938
♫ I cried when you leave and I keep on reminiscing
about the happy times we had ♫

56
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:14,200
♫ The regrets that I have will last me a lifetime ♫

57
00:06:14,294 --> 00:06:21,108
♫ After all of those hardships, we are no longer young ♫

58
00:06:21,108 --> 00:06:24,519
♫ I'm doomed to live in loneliness forever ♫

59
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:28,000
♫ It's bad but I can't help it ♫

60
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:34,400
[General's Manor]
♫ Are you suffering just like me? Are in turmoil as well? ♫

61
00:06:34,437 --> 00:06:40,630
♫ After all the boom and bust, I have lost all hope ♫

62
00:06:42,616 --> 00:06:46,081
General Fu, let me feed the princess.

63
00:06:46,081 --> 00:06:49,171
You've been awake for three days and three nights.

64
00:07:07,693 --> 00:07:12,959
♫ Let's drink to forget our worries, and bottoms up... ♫

65
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:16,799
♫ for you who have turned grey ♫

66
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,954
You may leave now.

67
00:07:18,954 --> 00:07:21,087
Yes, General Fu.

68
00:07:27,796 --> 00:07:29,656
Rong Le.

69
00:07:30,969 --> 00:07:33,607
Are you punishing me...

70
00:07:33,607 --> 00:07:36,203
or is Heaven punishing me?

71
00:07:37,153 --> 00:07:39,713
I can't bear this kind of punishment.

72
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,392
As long as you can wake up,

73
00:07:45,668 --> 00:07:47,648
I don't care...

74
00:07:48,471 --> 00:07:50,162
if you don't love me,

75
00:07:50,163 --> 00:07:52,299
I don't care if you leave me...

76
00:07:52,299 --> 00:07:54,204
or...

77
00:07:55,053 --> 00:07:57,197
even hate me.

78
00:07:57,996 --> 00:08:00,222
I don't care as long as you can wake up.

79
00:08:10,873 --> 00:08:14,537
- Emperor Wen watches from Heaven,
- Emperor Wen watches from Heaven,

80
00:08:14,538 --> 00:08:18,362
- shining bright, and bringing us light.
- shining bright, and bringing us light.

81
00:08:18,363 --> 00:08:22,067
- The Zhou kingdom has its age,
- The Zhou kingdom has its age,

82
